                <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-7">
                    The register of digital identity and attribute services is a public list of
                    government-registered organisations that provide digital identity services
                    certified against the
                    <a class="govuk-link" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/uk-digital-identity-and-attributes-trust-framework">UK digital identity and attributes trust framework</a>.
                </p>

             
                <h2 class="govuk-heading-m" id="use-for">
                    What you can use this service for
                </h2>
           

                <p class="govuk-body">Anyone can access the register to:</p>
                <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet govuk-list--spaced">
                    <li>view the full list of registered digital identity services</li>
                    <li>search for a specific digital identity provider or service</li>
                    <li>check if a provider holds a valid certificate for its services</li>
                    <li>filter providers or services based on your requirements</li>
                </ul>

                <p class="govuk-body">
                    If a provider’s certificate expires, or they fail to meet the requirements of the UK digital identity and attributes trust framework, they are removed from the register.
                </p>
            
             
                <h2 class="govuk-heading-m" id="cannot-use-for">
                    What you cannot use this service for
                </h2>

                <p class="govuk-body">You cannot use this service to find:</p>
                <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet govuk-list--spaced">
                    <li>commercial information about a provider, such as pricing for services</li>
                    <li>additional details about a provider, such as their size or experience</li>
                </ul>
              
             
